Fire at Durban factory. Picture: RESCUE CARE A raging fire has broken out at a factory near the Bluff in Durban. Firefighters arrived on the scene on Friday morning. Rescue Care Services Garrith Jamieson said: &#8220;The fire is spreading and fire rescue workers are on scene trying to contain the blaze. Paramedics are assessing some patients.&#8221; This is a developing story. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share